title: Krissy Chula AKA Krystal Smith
itunes:title: Krissy Chula AKA Krystal Smith
description:
Krystal is an actress and comedian known for her hilarious takes on Nicole Kidman, Miley Cyrus, and Lana Del Rey.  Whitney and Krystal cover everything from Tom Cruise to magician anatomy and really no further description here can do it justice.  Krystal's new Fox show Welcome to Flatch is coming soon.
